POST /v1/transactions/{businessTransactionId}/verify

Locked architectural decision

This schema aligns with your Verification Model:

Verification always evaluates the entire Execution Trust Record.
A single verified field provides the overall result.
The checks object exposes the integrity result for each trust artifact, allowing clients to identify exactly what failed while preserving a deterministic, whole-record verification model.

